Webtalk is a presentation framework targeted as simplified replacement for Power Point. If you know how to develop web pages (HTML / CSS), then you can use Webtalk to develop your presentation. 

Here is a presentation on Webtalk developed using the Webtalk framework:

http://bobcravens.com/presos/webtalk


Here is another example of a Webtalk presentation. I gave this at MvcConf.

http://bobcravens.com/presos/trucktracker



Enjoy.

Bob Cravens